content: Data import from Google Workspace to {{organizationName}} {{productName}} is complete!

comment.text: This translation key is used for a completion message when data import from Google Workspace is finished. The message informs users that the import process has been completed successfully and displays the product name of the {{organizationName}}. It appears in a dialog or notification after a successful import operation.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Greek translation places 'του' between 'στο' and '{{organizationName}}'. While grammatically valid, it might be more natural to place it after '{{organizationName}}' for better readability in a user interface.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Η εισαγωγή δεδομένων από το Google Workspace στο {{organizationName}} του {{productName}} ολοκληρώθηκε!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The colon and space after "{{productName}}" are awkward in Finnish. It breaks the flow of the sentence.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Tietojen tuonti Google Workspacesta {{organizationName}} {{productName}}-tuotteeseen on suoritettu!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Armenian translation uses a hyphen (-) between 'Google Workspace' and 'ից'. While understandable, using an en dash (–) might be more appropriate for this type of connection, signifying a relationship or association rather than a direct connection.
The phrase 'A importação de dados...' is grammatically incorrect. It should be 'A importação dos dados...' or simply 'A importação...'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A importação dos dados do Google Workspace para o {{organizationName}} {{productName}} foi concluída!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The sentence starts with 'A' (feminine article) instead of 'A importação' (The import). This is grammatically incorrect in Portuguese.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: A importação de dados do Google Workspace para o {{organizationName}} {{productName}} foi concluída!

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'date' is used instead of 'datele'. 'Date' is plural and 'datele' is the correct plural form for 'data'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Import datele din Google Workspace în {{organizationName}} {{productName}} este finalizat!
